title: New Star Trek GO SMS Popup
creator: star-E

extendedInfo.description: Enhance your texting experience with this new Popup theme. This will perfectly compliment the New Star Trek GO SMS Theme. With this, you can enjoy the look and feel of the computer displays in the new Star Trek movies (2009 and 2013 Into Darkness PCAP style to replace the standard LCARS). This theme is ideal for true fans or anyone who wants a sleek Sci-Fi look.Directions:1. After installing this theme, open GO SMS Pro -> press the menu button -> Themes -> GO Popup -> Click "Turn on". If you have turned on the GO Popup feature, skip this step.2. Open GO SMS Pro -> press the menu button -> Themes -> GO Popup -> Installed tab, choose the theme screeshot to apply. When receiving a new message, you will see the new GO Popup inteface.  ****So, text someone and wait for a reply to check it out****Tips: Please make sure that you have installed GO SMS Pro V4.67 or above.////****After install don't press 'Open'. Also, don't use the shortcut icon that is created. Just apply the theme in the GO SMS Pro settings.****////Also look for:New Star Trek Go Launcher ThemeNew Star Trek Keyboard ThemeNew Star Trek GO Contacts / Dialer ThemeNew Star Trek Go Locker ThemeNew Star Trek GOWidget ThemeNew Star Trek Go SMS ThemeNew Star Trek Live WallpaperNew Star Trek GO FontsNew Star Trek clock & battery skin (available free in Beautiful Widgets theme picker)*clock updated to v2*As you can see, I have a very complete theme pack suite to customize the whole phone / tablet for all parts of common use.To get informed when I release new Star Trek themes, follow me on twitter. @SethSteen or Facebook http://www.facebook.com/new.star.trek.theme Also, if you're a Trekkie I would appreciate it if you could support my work by clicking 'g+1' or sharing it on your social networks.If you like my work, PLEASE leave me a nice review to help me continue. Too many people never read the directions and leave a bad review saying, "It doesn't work".*If you are having trouble and the contact developer link isn't working, please contact me at seththomaslewis@gmail.com That is my personal email so I can get notifications right away and offer the fastest support.
